{"tid":1684122,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"(孤獨圍爐)呢一刻嘅你，有冇覺得孤獨？(2)","createTime":"2019-10-31T02:53:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T14:42:34.000Z","uid":92200,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e482c76660e9b9f8ec99b9cee69765dbe1d4b462","tid":1684122,"uid":92200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:53:39.000Z","msg":"繼續傾下孤獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望收集大家孤獨既故事<br />\n<br />\n任何人都會孤獨，年紀越大就會越孤獨<br />\n有朋友又好，人群之中都會寂寞空虛<br />\n無朋友又好，一心期望想識更多朋友但未必每個人都同自己連結到<br />\n最後，當孤獨變成習慣，就好易好病<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論點孤獨都好，呢刻都會陪住大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1583101/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1583101/page/1</a><br />\n(孤獨圍爐)呢一刻嘅你，有冇覺得孤獨？"},{"pid":"9cd3cdb0b05574b13fa7ed26aa4a614f52d8493e","tid":1684122,"uid":92200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:05:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12a6d3101f995f03f6755751886edc5d9f535d8","tid":1684122,"uid":92200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:28:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5d8b88c65e62c2dcecfb03811ca67f74a229fd","tid":1684122,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去兩個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依兩個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />